召唤一个tag为awa的隐身盔甲架：/summon minecraft:armor_stand ~ ~1 ~ {Tags:["awa"],CustomNameVisible:0b,Invulnerable:1b,PersistenceRequired:1b,Invisible:1,Rotation:[0f],Pose:{Head:[0f,0f,0f],Body:[0f,0f,0f],LeftArm:[0f,0f,0f],RightArm:[0f,0f,0f],LeftLeg:[0f,0f,0f],RightLeg:[0f,0f,0f]}}


重复执行：将tag为awa的生物tp到tag为dui_zhang的生物：/execute as @e[tag=dui_zhang] at @d run tp @e[tag=awa] ~ ~ ~


重复执行：感应tag为awa的生物周围没有一个tag为dui_zhang和类型为掠夺者的生物说1，/execute as @e[tag=awa] at @s run execute as @e[type=pillager,tag=!dui_zhang,distance=1..1] at @s run say 1
